{
  "stem": "23942.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I used to come to their house and sit down sometimes, a few of her friends.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember I was sitting in one of her friend's house and then I remember seeing plants.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it made me feel good looking at the plants.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I realized there's some life out there, that not everybody is hiding.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I see that it was a nice, warm house and I felt good for the temporarily.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they let me stay there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember one day another friend came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they wanted to take me to I should help in their house and they'll keep me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I started to walk out of the house, like one connected me to the other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then this lady who wanted to take me to her house happened to live in the very center of the town where the Jewish people once lived.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I knew I would have been recognized, one way or another.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I actually started to walk with her on the road going to her home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "On the way I suddenly woke up and I realized, my gosh.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If I go where she told me she's living, I'm going to be killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I said, no thank you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Not so well, I said, I changed my mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because I realized what I have to do for me is what my brain tells me to do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The brain that I had at that-- in other words, the seykhl that I had at that time, the common sense, whatever I had, told me that I shouldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I listened to my common sense.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whether it was the smartest or not, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All I know is that my common sense told me, don't do this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
